<i>"Never leave for tomorrow what you can do today."</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ucloud1011.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cloud1011</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/15/02 3:18:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3903.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Suggestions</span><hr size=1> Nice, drop the bracers get cultural bracers, i think elves can wear human cultural. Don't buy them, farm the components not hard to get. <br>
<br>
Also sell the vah shir earing you have and get 35hp ones if you can't get better. Not sure about pricing on your server if you can get a mosquito leg or hammered golden hoop...etc<br>
<br>
Spend a day in ME hunting cotorie and get a grodan's idol instead of goranga... HUGE upgrade that can be done with one group.<br>
<br>
Get rid of that mask and get a Death Mask of the Elysians if you can, otherwise get crystal spider eyes.<br>
<br>
I'd keep your current weapons if you are MT stun is a good agro proc for a pre-HoT guild<br>
<br>
I personally preferr the Shrouded Medallion that drops in ME off of 4-arms to the glimmering mithral torque....Medallion is 12ac 5str 10svm 5svf 5svc and fairly common. You could prolly get the Grodan's idol and this in a day. the idol and medallion are both no drop tho.<br>
<br>
Get rid of the spider Fur Cloak and if get either a cloak of the maelstrom or hooded black cloak. Or if you are able go to Chardok and get Heiro cloak.<br>
<br>
Overall go for raw hp/ac/resists there's always a shammy or two to give ya the str/dex/sta/agi ya want.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukiyallmanebloodcry.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KiyallmaneBloodcry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 269<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/16/02 12:09:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3903.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~bass72/_uimages/1C.gif hieght=140 width=113></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Suggestions</span><hr size=1> I worship Tunare, I cannot wear fierce heraldic.  The closest thing I could wear is Full Mirthil (High elf cultural), non-imbued bracer is something like 25 ac, 30 hp/mana.  Not sure if it's worth the 10k+ to me.  <br>
